0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"我早一個星期摷返床頭部封塵5s嚟玩<br />\n應該3-4年冇開過機<br />\n電都叉唔着咁滯<br />\n一開到機好似仲行緊iOS 9<br />\n但指紋解鎖中咗都要入密碼先得<br />\n我入哂我電話上面會用嘅密碼都fail<br />\n(我用customise numeric code)<br />\n最後開始鎖機<br />\n結果要連iTunes force restart <br />\nUpgrade 咗做iOS 12<br />\n開得返佢叫我入返之前雙重認證過嗰個apple id <br />\n如果唔係都係磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後當然成功用得返<br />\n但入面冇咗咩資料就唔知了<br />\n好彩我咩都有定期back up<br />\n<br />\nPs 連iTunes 時揀部之前連過trusted 嘅電腦先有機會救到最多資料<br />\n如果冇就只可以洗機重生"},{"pid":"0e7c619ce648bd3b60c47ae07acd0ec6ba7ca961","tid":853894,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"搵FBI破解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0cd771e4c7d7a39e08c3e739bd7c0915295c36","tid":853894,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"比返部機人啦屌你"},{"pid":"6b9d28e79021d830bb0a5f1ee5ce9c3abb89701a","tid":853894,"uid":194130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"25e0a4cb13cdc02bf1ef27f646b5d6446f62d92c","tid":853894,"uid":1374,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"想知日日都用電話既人點解會唔記得個密碼<br />\n只係得一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾番人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"佢可能用開Face ID<br />\n點知去完韓國一轉........."},{"pid":"c071439523c7f593bd0ea4f693cf6e85bd996d41","tid":853894,"uid":209736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25e0a4cb13cdc02bf1ef27f646b5d6446f62d92c","tid":853894,"uid":1374,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:02:07.000Z","msg":"想知日日都用電話既人點解會唔記得個密碼<br />\n只係得一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s